7:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=79bb0be5\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"},{"pid":"a0a27aa1b18bc5ff03d2a1ff4afa192ea5994538","tid":1363771,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:49:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66660eec1c436712bf1e2968302ea48a5d9c44f0","tid":1363771,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c81d71b524115e9d96d1254450bb9801a23554a","tid":1363771,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f2a0e581a1a5ebd728e53c6f085bfc64417288","tid":1363771,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bef1a66e221520b1fa6959602d4816d4bec7543","tid":1363771,"uid":280666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"宗教集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而回到最初的起點，究竟「報佳音」本身，是否會因為沒取得警方的不反對通知書，以至會被視為是非法集會？根據法例，其實已有明確的答案！《公安條例》中第2條的釋義中，其實已就「集會」一詞作出極清晰不過的定義，指出「但完全為以下目的而召集或組織的聚集或集結」，就不包括在法例規管的「集會」之中，其中a項就是：<br />\n<br />\n為社交、康樂、文化、學術、教育、宗教或慈善目的而進行的聚集或集結，或真誠地擬為討論屬社交、康樂、文化、學術、教育、宗教、慈善、專業、業務或商務性質的論題，而以會議或研討會形式進行的聚集或集結；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/71648/范析852│《公安條例》豁免規管「報佳音」-警指控/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F71648%2F%E8%8C%83%E6%9E%90852%E2%94%82%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E8%A6%8F%E7%AE%A1%E3%80%8C%E5%A0%B1%E4%BD%B3%E9%9F%B3%E3%80%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%2F&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=d29a1f85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/71648/范析852│《公安條例》豁免規管「報佳音」-警指控/</a>"},{"pid":"f6bdb308b8d964856f9b06cfcb2df0809cfeca7f","tid":1363771,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138667fb7f4c7975061c8fa2b115e0c435f6ae3f","tid":1363771,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc690bb4ba6fc2007cea6ee2e633f145cb2e8285","tid":1363771,"uid":66569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:02:00.000Z","msg":"陳雲：為了配合陳雲提倡的流水社運，軍閥兵團拒絕發出星期六在元朗的不反對通知書，令這次行街無組織、無領袖、無dress code、無糾察、無路線、無開始、無結束。究竟是誰在示威都不知道。<br />\n天才呀。"},{"pid":"59e7a401fbaa13e2dc9aa6021d723ca9c3ea2c68","tid":1363771,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f43c0ed040564a455de89a676d385f7d98c1d61b","tid":1363771,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6902ecf1ab8b05d50ce0390e41ccbbbe918c7f31","tid":1363771,"uid":105905,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"宗教集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/big